<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- #1a5cff -->
    <div
      style="
        width: 100%;
        height: 70px;
        display: block;
        background-color: #1a5cff;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding-top: 26px;
      "
    >
      <a
        style="
          text-decoration: none;
          color: #fff;
          font-size: 30px;
          font-family: 'Arial';
          font-weight: bold;
        "
        href="http://devsparkle.ir"
      >
        devsparkle.ir
      </a>
    </div>
    <div
      style="
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      "
    >
      <p
        style="
          width: 100%;
          display: block;
          color: #555;
          font-weight: bold;
          font-size: 16px;
          text-decoration: none;
        "
        dir="rtl"
      >
        سلام
        <span style="color: #1a5cff; text-decoration: none"><%= email %></span>
        عزیز
      </p>
      <p
        style="
          width: 100%;
          display: block;
          padding-right: 20px;
          color: #555;
          font-weight: bold;
          font-size: 18px;
        "
        dir="rtl"
      >
        برایی تایید ایمیل روی دکمه زیر کلیک کنید...
      </p>
      <br />
      <a
        style="
          padding: 15px 30px;
          background-color: #fff;
          border: 2px solid #1a5cff;
          color: #1a5cff;
          border-radius: 5px;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-weight: bold;
          font-size: 17px;
        "
        href="<%= front_end_address %>/verify_email/<%= token %>?email=<%= email %>"
        >تایید ایمیل</a
      >
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
